Stellar Students Celebration
March 2nd, 2019
Teachers, students and community members are invited to honor our local Stellar Students and celebrate with us on the Base Lodge Deck on Saturday March 2nd at 12:30pm. Ceremony will include a hot cocoa toast, group photos, live music and more. 
Schedule of Events - Base Lodge Deck
12:00pm: Stellar Students sign in on the deck
12:30pm: Ceremony & photos
12:45pm - 3:30pm: Live music by Jacked up Lake Tahoe
Remember that all Stellar Students pass refund requests need to be submitted to guest services by February 28, 2019. View the Stellar Students page for more information. 
